{"tid":433103,"cid":16,"subCid":0,"title":"覺唔覺臭雞黎講，煙燻黎講最吸引","createTime":"2017-10-12T06:02:34.000Z","updateTime":"2017-10-13T00:48:08.000Z","uid":74981,"like":0,"dislike":3,"uniUserReply":4,"replies":[{"pid":"108cef64a0316dbdcf5eb42c39ff48619eabe6c3","tid":433103,"uid":74981,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-12T06:02:34.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/bomb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"10a750c39d5517f47b4d64ed7cbe40460d1dacab","tid":433103,"uid":19762,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-12T06:09:36.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://addapinch.com/wp-content/blogs.dir/3/files/2013/06/how-to-smoke-whole-chicken-DSC_3421.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Faddapinch.com%2Fwp-content%2Fblogs.dir%2F3%2Ffiles%2F2013%2F06%2Fhow-to-smoke-whole-chicken-DSC_3421.jpg&h=6431f834&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"f6de19d287c1eee4a26d999072b13df11c2c674e","tid":433103,"uid":21423,"like":0,"dislike":2,"score":-2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-12T06:43:34.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"6f87abcaab20bce8d758ad04f6d9e9bd7067670a","tid":433103,"uid":55077,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-12T06:44:58.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/surprise.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/big/surprise.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"56a38294a4ee8502507673d92b7e3f203f229b42","tid":433103,"uid":74981,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-13T00:02:26.000Z","msg":"等本癲狗介紹下肥絲到底係何方神聖<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/10.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n話到明肥絲, 緊係肥閪一條啦. 咁到底佢有幾撚肥? 不如睇下佢既自我介紹啦:<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<strong><ins>原來男人老狗得果158CM高, 168磅!</ins></strong><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://s13.postimg.org/wg5s0sjbb/Truth_Weight.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fs13.postimg.org%2Fwg5s0sjbb%2FTruth_Weight.png&h=4237dead&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n唔怪得佢成日咁憎本癲狗啦, 因為本癲狗高條肥閪一截, 又冇條肥閪咁撚肥, 咁佢咪妒忌我承機攻擊我囉. 誰不知天網恢恢, 咁都俾我搵到條肥閪既自爆POST, 咁佢自己攞黎柒, 我都幫佢唔撚到啦<img src=\"https://media.giphy.com/media/3oKIP8hJYG1uPqXPby/giphy.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fmedia.giphy.com%2Fmedia%2F3oKIP8hJYG1uPqXPby%2Fgiphy.gif&h=6424ffd1&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n既然佢唔敢POST自己身型既相, 就等本癲狗幫佢一把啦, 男人身高158CM, 168磅既身型大慨係咁:<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://s15.postimg.org/fwrlxvnrv/image.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fs15.postimg.org%2Ffwrlxvnrv%2Fimage.jpg&h=1787cf3f&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://media.giphy.com/media/3oKIP8hJYG1uPqXPby/giphy.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fmedia.giphy.com%2Fmedia%2F3oKIP8hJYG1uPqXPby%2Fgiphy.gif&h=6424ffd1&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<strong><ins>肥絲原來係肥佬扮肥婆!</ins></strong><br />\n<br />\n大家唔知一定以為肥絲係女人啦, NO NO NO, 其實佢係男人黎, 睇下, 佢又自爆啦:<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://s22.postimg.org/i8z8gk3xt/Screenshot_2017-05-27-09-23-42.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fs22.postimg.org%2Fi8z8gk3xt%2FScreenshot_2017-05-27-09-23-42.png&h=6a188dbf&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n男人老狗幻想自己係女人都算啦, 但竟然幻想自已係肥矮臭柒毒既肥婆, 誤導各位, 真係又核突, 又變態<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n不過, 補充一點, 佢肥矮臭柒毒係事實, 不過係肥矮臭柒毒既麻甩佬, 並唔係肥婆囉.<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/15.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<strong><ins>肥絲自爆係畜牲?</ins></strong><br />\n<br />\n原來肥絲除左肥矮臭柒毒之外, 原來仲好撚似猩猩<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> , 各位睇下:<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://s8.postimg.org/4uvmleq7p/Screenshot_2017-05-27-10-13-54.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fs8.postimg.org%2F4uvmleq7p%2FScreenshot_2017-05-27-10-13-54.png&h=0463833c&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<strong><ins>肥絲年齡之謎&hellip;</ins></strong><br />\n<br />\n其實肥絲咁撚ON9, 大家估下佢幾歲<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 哩層本癲狗都無法判斷, 請各位巴打分析下:<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n84日前, 牠27歲<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://s8.postimg.org/472926oth/27_84.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fs8.postimg.org%2F472926oth%2F27_84.png&h=71a99850&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n110日前, 牠30歲<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://s8.postimg.org/n706uevsl/30_110.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fs8.postimg.org%2Fn706uevsl%2F30_110.png&h=4c570172&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n154日前, 牠24歲<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://s18.postimg.org/gf9qghnsp/24_154.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fs18.postimg.org%2Fgf9qghnsp%2F24_154.png&h=0a9f11af&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n170日前, 牠31歲<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://s14.postimg.org/n1ezatkgh/31_170.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fs14.postimg.org%2Fn1ezatkgh%2F31_170.png&h=92e0b647&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n175日前, 牠25歲<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://s1.postimg.org/9j52syre7/25_175.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fs1.postimg.org%2F9j52syre7%2F25_175.png&h=7727adf8&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n179日前, 牠27歲<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://s4.postimg.org/dulrpdl7x/27_179.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fs4.postimg.org%2Fdulrpdl7x%2F27_179.png&h=0127f621&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n180日前, 牠30歲<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://s29.postimg.org/d7irbcnc7/30_180.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fs29.postimg.org%2Fd7irbcnc7%2F30_180.png&h=0a4a9f01&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n肥絲, 好心你寫野MAKE SENSE D 啦, 成日學人講邏輯, 話人唔撚夠你講, 咁宜家你又解唔解釋到哩個呀傻閪? 你都係匿番入你老母個閪扮睇唔到算啦, 無謂衝出黎柒啦<img src=\"https://media.giphy.com/media/3oKIP8hJYG1uPqXPby/giphy.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fmedia.giphy.com%2Fmedia%2F3oKIP8hJYG1uPqXPby%2Fgiphy.gif&h=6424ffd1&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<strong><ins>癲狗感想:</ins></strong><br />\n<br />\n肥絲, 其實你做埋咁多野，大費周章，起哂我底，圖文並茂，本癲狗真係好開心架，因為好少可真係有d狗俾我撚到發哂火，非係要整鳩我不可，我的目的已經達到了<img src=\"https://media.giphy.com/media/3oKIP8hJYG1uPqXPby/giphy.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fmedia.giphy.com%2Fmedia%2F3oKIP8hJYG1uPqXPby%2Fgiphy.gif&h=6424ffd1&s={SIZE}\" />雖然你咁有心機整咁大篇垃圾批鬥文出黎，但來來去去都係得果幾條基佬撐你，全世界都當你傻閪，唔想理你，咁你都唔洗遷怒於我架? 你估你又好好咩? 男人老狗幻想自己係女都算，但幻想自己係d狗都唔屌既油脂肥婆，你係唔係老母中撚在幅射生到你心理變態呀? 真係人唔笑，狗都吠呀<img src=\"https://media.giphy.com/media/3oKIP8hJYG1uPqXPby/giphy.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fmedia.giphy.com%2Fmedia%2F3oKIP8hJYG1uPqXPby%2Fgiphy.gif&h=6424ffd1&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n我知你老母生到你又肥又基又弱智，現實廢鳩一條，只能做鍵盤戰士，你好憎佢，想佢日日俾人屌，但你都唔洗借本癲狗過橋架? 你老母做雞，我已經盡量幫襯多d，屌到佢閪皮都化埋，你唔洗再引其他人屌佢啦，做人唔好咁撚不孝先得架<img src=\"https://media.giphy.com/media/3oKIP8hJYG1uPqXPby/giphy.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fmedia.giphy.com%2Fmedia%2F3oKIP8hJYG1uPqXPby%2Fgiphy.gif&h=6424ffd1&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n係唔係因為你自小就因為肥矮臭柒毒所以俾人排斥, 冇朋友, 冇人注意, 所以一上網就要做鍵盤戰士, 引人注意, 認為嘈交贏左就係&quot;打贏仗&quot;, 將自己開既post叫做&quot;戰場&quot;. 可惜, 你對住本癲狗就從來都未贏過一仗, 連自己自以為擅長既地方都俾人打敗, 唔怪得你咁憎我啦. <img src=\"https://media.giphy.com/media/3oKIP8hJYG1uPqXPby/giphy.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fmedia.giphy.com%2Fmedia%2F3oKIP8hJYG1uPqXPby%2Fgiphy.gif&h=6424ffd1&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"8362c11f2c0ab4ef7c5ba620806ef4a22481eb0c","tid":433103,"uid":74981,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-13T00:02:56.000Z","msg":"肥閪你篇垃圾冇人睇架啦, 睇我哩篇好過啦<img src=\"https://media.giphy.com/media/3oKIP8hJYG1uPqXPby/giphy.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fmedia.giphy.com%2Fmedia%2F3oKIP8hJYG1uPqXPby%2Fgiphy.gif&h=6424ffd1&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n為左大家更了解位連登隻畜牲既所作所為, 本癲狗帶大家進行深入探討<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n網名：肥絲大隻<br />\n編號：21423<br />\n身高：158厘米<br />\n體重：168磅<br />\n居住：估計應該係狗籠 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n特徵：矮、肥、柒、毒、臭<br />\n嗜好：幻想自己係律師, 雄辯淊淊, 可惜除左佢班狗同伴以外, 無人想理佢, 連ADMIN都當鳩佢傻仔無視佢<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<strong><ins>1. 肥閪黑歷史, 得罪人多, 犯眾憎</ins></strong><br />\n<br />\n<strong>肥絲大隻糾正ABC張曦雯英文</strong><br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://lihkg.com/thread/110910/page/1\" target=\"_blank\">https://lihkg.com/thread/110910/page/1</a><br />\n<br />\n其實肥絲柒都唔係第一日架啦, 不過估唔到佢真係柒到以為自己有料Challenge人地張曦雯d英文, 人地話哂完成小學四年級後跟屋企人移民至美國芝加哥咁耐, 英文會差得過條肥閪? 肥閪小學四年班果陣做緊咩呀? 應該仲係度on99比同學排斥杯葛緊咋<img src=\"https://media.giphy.com/media/3oKIP8hJYG1uPqXPby/giphy.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fmedia.giphy.com%2Fmedia%2F3oKIP8hJYG1uPqXPby%2Fgiphy.gif&h=6424ffd1&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<strong>肥絲大隻帶頭block人</strong><br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://lihkg.com/thread/162651/page/1\" target=\"_blank\">https://lihkg.com/thread/162651/page/1</a><br />\n<br />\n柒頭肥絲又唔知做咩on9得罪人, 連續比38頁既巴打絲打毫不留情地block<img src=\"https://media.giphy.com/media/3oKIP8hJYG1uPqXPby/giphy.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fmedia.giphy.com%2Fmedia%2F3oKIP8hJYG1uPqXPby%2Fgiphy.gif&h=6424ffd1&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://s23.postimg.org/a8mntgqbf/Block.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fs23.postimg.org%2Fa8mntgqbf%2FBlock.jpg&h=897724c1&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n佢柒既程度真係史無前例, 哩點佢可以贏到本癲狗<img src=\"https://media.giphy.com/media/3oKIP8hJYG1uPqXPby/giphy.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fmedia.giphy.com%2Fmedia%2F3oKIP8hJYG1uPqXPby%2Fgiphy.gif&h=6424ffd1&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<strong><ins>2. 就因為肥閪人氣差, 於是就想藉著打擊本癲狗上位, 可惜各位巴打絲打眼晴係雪亮既, 大部份都支持本癲狗, 除左少數畜牲會企係佢果邊之外</ins></strong><img src=\"https://media.giphy.com/media/3oKIP8hJYG1uPqXPby/giphy.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fmedia.giphy.com%2Fmedia%2F3oKIP8hJYG1uPqXPby%2Fgiphy.gif&h=6424ffd1&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://s3.postimg.org/ysubhparn/Screenshot_2017-05-29-21-32-28.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fs3.postimg.org%2Fysubhparn%2FScreenshot_2017-05-29-21-32-28.png&h=5502e14e&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n係佢對本癲狗作出第一輪攻擊前, 已經有好多巴打支持本癲狗同屌鳩條肥閪:<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://s15.postimg.org/qnp5kvax7/Before_1st_attack.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fs15.postimg.org%2Fqnp5kvax7%2FBefore_1st_attack.jpg&h=1bfadd26&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n本來肥絲被本癲狗撚到潛哂水, 不過佢又唔服, 於是作出零星反抗:<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://s23.postimg.org/f916lhd5n/Screenshot_2017-05-29-21-23-19.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fs23.postimg.org%2Ff916lhd5n%2FScreenshot_2017-05-29-21-23-19.png&h=43f474d6&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n可惜各位都無視佢整左三日三夜既成果, 繼續支持本癲狗同屌鳩條肥閪:<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://s17.postimg.org/xckosaaz3/After_1st_Attack.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fs17.postimg.org%2Fxckosaaz3%2FAfter_1st_Attack.jpg&h=8043c150&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n於是肥絲又被我撚到忍唔住, 發表第二輪零星攻勢, 大慨就係補充左幾頁廢話之類的...<img src=\"https://media.giphy.com/media/3oKIP8hJYG1uPqXPby/giphy.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fmedia.giphy.com%2Fmedia%2F3oKIP8hJYG1uPqXPby%2Fgiphy.gif&h=6424ffd1&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://s23.postimg.org/7vw9ovpxn/Screenshot_2017-05-29-21-26-35.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fs23.postimg.org%2F7vw9ovpxn%2FScreenshot_2017-05-29-21-26-35.png&h=08511494&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n可惜各位都繼續無視佢 (除左幾件微不足道既蛋散), 繼續支持本癲狗同屌鳩條肥閪:<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://s1.postimg.org/6bqhp0qb3/After_2nd_attack.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fs1.postimg.org%2F6bqhp0qb3%2FAfter_2nd_attack.jpg&h=3c1d117a&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n其實肥絲你同你班狗契仔唔好再作無謂既反抗啦, 你咁做同想用流星錘打架戰機落黎有咩分別呢? 以下係肥絲既抗強而無力既反抗圖<img src=\"https://media.giphy.com/media/3oKIP8hJYG1uPqXPby/giphy.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fmedia.giphy.com%2Fmedia%2F3oKIP8hJYG1uPqXPby%2Fgiphy.gif&h=6424ffd1&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://s14.postimg.org/gzt7y84vl/0_GAC6_S0_ATJ.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fs14.postimg.org%2Fgzt7y84vl%2F0_GAC6_S0_ATJ.gif&h=a4d0a651&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<strong><ins>3. 肥絲無力還撃既狼狽相 (柒左又唔認):</ins></strong><br />\n<br />\n自從本癲狗拆穿條肥閪得果158cm高同168磅重仲有大量on9自爆之後, 肥絲無力還擊, 只能以&quot;真心左&quot;, &quot;假膠&quot;等來反擊來掩飾自己既&quot;糗&quot;<img src=\"https://media.giphy.com/media/3oKIP8hJYG1uPqXPby/giphy.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fmedia.giphy.com%2Fmedia%2F3oKIP8hJYG1uPqXPby%2Fgiphy.gif&h=6424ffd1&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://s21.postimg.org/6svpph81j/Excuse.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fs21.postimg.org%2F6svpph81j%2FExcuse.jpg&h=8bbd2f7e&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n4. 肥絲同佢班狗契仔既基本有以下既特質, 所以極度討厭本癲狗用以下詞彙形容佢地, 因為崩口狗忌崩口兜嘛<img src=\"https://media.giphy.com/media/3oKIP8hJYG1uPqXPby/giphy.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fmedia.giphy.com%2Fmedia%2F3oKIP8hJYG1uPqXPby%2Fgiphy.gif&h=6424ffd1&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n- 喜歡自己老母俾人屌<br />\n<br />\n- 老母是性工作者<br />\n<br />\n- 本身係狗 / 食屎狗 / 喜歡被撚<br />\n<br />\n- 小學雞<br />\n<br />\n- 容易被撚到嬲嬲豬/發嬲/發火<br />\n<br />\n- 肥西/肥閪<br />\n<br />\n- 基友/基佬<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n總結: 其實肥絲都只不過係條人格唔健全既傻閪姐, 大家高抬貴手, 唔好玩到佢咁盡<img src=\"https://media.giphy.com/media/3oKIP8hJYG1uPqXPby/giphy.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fmedia.giphy.com%2Fmedia%2F3oKIP8hJYG1uPqXPby%2Fgiphy.gif&h=6424ffd1&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"8fba2e5ad11f34279f7e1c2f23e4a0f38e753f27","tid":433103,"uid":74981,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-13T00:03:16.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"co