hot_2017-09-29-14-11-56.png&h=0f10322e&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n可惜條傻鳩唔明白一個道理，<strong><span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">就係明眼人一睇就知，肥鳩其實就係故事主角既投射</span></span></strong>，例如牠本身又肥又矮，就會引用d主角又肥又矮既故事。<br />\n<br />\n又例如肥鳩根本係文盲唔識中文，所以故事主角寫錯字佢都會懵然不知，照單全收<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"36195345a833140ef0b3fc776409dc3c96a8ec44","tid":433103,"uid":21423,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-13T00:07:23.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"c5112f0582adb4e956b96d588072acd0626a58e4","tid":433103,"uid":74981,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-13T00:10:41.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><strong>肥鳩大隻其實傻得好勻秦，所謂既正評得果幾百個讚就沾沾自喜，好似成世未俾人讚過咁<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/10.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n嗱，本癲狗一個玩鳩你既post都900幾個正皮啦:</strong></span></span><br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://lihkg.com/thread/261676/page/1?ref=android\" target=\"_blank\">https://lihkg.com/thread/261676/page/1?ref=android</a><br />\n<br />\n<strong><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">你條傻鳩俾我玩都可以拎黎自豪，將佢演繹成我靠你，咁撚呀Q精神，咁你繼續留係度俾我玩啦，咁你咪俾人玩當贏囉<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/10.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n依你個on9邏輯，你條肥鳩咪又係靠人打錯字然後抽人水呃正評，你咪靠緊全連登既人上位囉懵撚<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/10.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></span></span></strong><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: orange;\"><strong><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">不過上極都上唔到反而呃左一推負皮同繼續做小丑俾大家恥笑<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/10.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></span></strong></span>"},{"pid":"2995b9a6ed13a4c292fb2a8fd5e213de307e8ef6","tid":433103,"uid":21423,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-13T00:28:32.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"4b5667484001a8ca191d735c743f8e41aa34123c","tid":433103,"uid":74981,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-13T00:48:08.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"